      "content": "hey, so i got a prescription for antibiotics for this skin infection i had. ive been taking them for 3 days now and the redness and swelling are totally gone. i feel way better. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to.",
