    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine if the infection is already gone. i read online that taking too many antibiotics can mess up your gut health and microbiome for a long time. if the symptoms are 100% gone, isn't it safer just to stop now so i don't cause more harm than good?",
