      "content": "i just don't like the idea of taking them for another week when there is literally nothing to treat. if i just take a double dose tomorrow to make up for the ones i missed, then stop, wouldn't that work? that way i'm still getting the medicine in but i'm not stuck on a 10-day cycle. what do you think?",
